# AutoDoc Local Rules

## Folder Structure

### Source Folders (in AutoDoc/)

```
DevTools/LegacyCodeTools/AutoDoc/
├── _css/                           # CSS stylesheets
│   ├── autodoc-shared.css          # Main shared styles
│   └── css-override.css            # Theme overrides
├── _images/                        # Image assets
│   ├── dedge.svg                      # FK logo (SVG)
│   └── dedge.ico                      # Favicon (ICO)
├── _js/                            # JavaScript files
│   ├── autodoc-diagram-controls.js # Diagram pan/zoom/fullscreen
│   ├── autodoc-mermaid-config.js   # Mermaid initialization & themes
│   └── svg-pan-zoom.js             # Pan-zoom library
├── _json/                          # Parser output data
│   ├── CblParseResult.json
│   ├── ScriptParseResult.json
│   ├── SqlParseResult.json
│   └── CSharpParseResult.json
├── _templates/                     # HTML templates
│   ├── batmmdtemplate.html
│   ├── cblmmdtemplate.html
│   ├── csharpmmdtemplate.html
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── ps1mmdtemplate.html
│   ├── rexmmdtemplate.html
│   ├── scriptindex.html
│   ├── sqlmmdtemplate.html
│   └── web.config
├── AutoDocBatchRunner.ps1          # Main generation script
├── Test-AutoDocGeneration.ps1      # Test wrapper script
└── _deploy.ps1                     # Deployment script
```

### Output Folder Structure

```
$env:OptPath\Webs\AutoDoc\
├── _css/                           # Copied from source
│   ├── autodoc-shared.css
│   └── css-override.css
├── _images/                        # Copied from source
│   ├── dedge.svg
│   └── dedge.ico
├── _js/                            # Copied from source
│   ├── autodoc-diagram-controls.js
│   ├── autodoc-mermaid-config.js
│   └── svg-pan-zoom.js
├── _json/                          # Parser results
│   ├── CblParseResult.json
│   ├── ScriptParseResult.json
│   ├── SqlParseResult.json
│   └── CSharpParseResult.json
├── _templates/                     # Copied from source
├── index.html                      # Copied from _templates/
├── web.config                      # Copied from _templates/
└── *.html                          # Generated documentation files
```

### Folder Naming Convention

**All asset folders use underscore prefix (`_`) instead of dot (`.`):**
- This ensures IIS serves static files without hidden segment filtering issues
- Folders starting with `.` are blocked by IIS by default
- Underscore prefix provides same visual "hidden" effect without IIS restrictions

### Folder Behavior During CleanRegenerate

**PRESERVED (never deleted):**
- `_css/` - CSS stylesheets
- `_js/` - JavaScript libraries
- `_images/` - Logo and favicon
- `index.html` - Index page
- `web.config` - IIS configuration

**CLEARED (content deleted, folder preserved):**
- `_json/` - Parser results (regenerated with fresh data)

---

## External JavaScript Architecture

### Problem Solved
The HTML templates had inline JavaScript with variable names like `type` which collided with template placeholders like `[type]`. This caused JavaScript syntax errors in generated HTML files.

### Solution: External JavaScript Files
All JavaScript is now in separate files in the `_js/` subfolder:
- `autodoc-diagram-controls.js` - Pan/zoom, fullscreen, theme switching
- `autodoc-mermaid-config.js` - Mermaid initialization and theme variables
- `svg-pan-zoom.js` - Third-party pan-zoom library

---

## Template Placeholder Reference

| Placeholder | Replacement | Purpose |
|-------------|-------------|---------|
| `[controlsscripturl]` | `./_js/autodoc-diagram-controls.js?v={timestamp}` | Diagram controls script |
| `[mermaidconfigurl]` | `./_js/autodoc-mermaid-config.js?v={timestamp}` | Mermaid config script |
| `[imageurl]` | `./_images/dedge.svg` | FK logo |
| `[iconurl]` | `./_images/dedge.ico` | Favicon |
| `[cssoverrideurl]` | `./_css/css-override.css` | CSS overrides |
| `[autodochomepageurl]` | `{baseUrl}/AutoDoc/index.html` | Home link |
| `[css]` | Contents of `_css/autodoc-shared.css` | Inline styles (injected) |
| `[type]` | Program type (e.g., "B - Batchprogram") | Metadata display only |

**Note:** JS URLs include cache-busting timestamps (`?v=yyyyMMddHHmm`) to prevent browser caching issues.

---

## Functions in autodoc-diagram-controls.js

**Theme Management:**
- `getPreferredTheme()` - Gets stored or system theme
- `setTheme(theme)` - Sets light/dark theme
- `updateThemeButtons(theme)` - Updates button active states
- `applyDarkModeLineStyles()` - Applies dark mode styling to SVG elements

**Diagram Controls:**
- `showDiagram(diagramType, btn)` - Switches between diagram tabs
- `initPanZoom(diagramType)` - Initializes svg-pan-zoom for a container
- `updateZoomIndicator(diagramType, level)` - Updates zoom percentage display
- `zoomIn(diagramType)`, `zoomOut(diagramType)` - Zoom controls
- `resetZoom(diagramType)`, `fitToScreen(diagramType)` - Reset/fit controls

**Mermaid 11 Fixes:**
- `fixForeignObjectDimensions(svg)` - Fixes 0x0 foreignObject elements
- `fixInvalidTransforms(svg)` - Fixes `translate(undefined, NaN)` errors
- `fixAllForeignObjects()` - Applies all fixes to all SVGs on page

**Advanced Features:**
- `openInNewWindow(diagramType)` - Opens diagram in new browser window
- `toggleFullscreen(diagramType)` - Opens fullscreen overlay
- `closeFullscreen()` - Closes fullscreen overlay
- `zoomInFullscreen()`, `zoomOutFullscreen()`, etc. - Fullscreen zoom controls

---

## Mermaid Configuration (autodoc-mermaid-config.js)

```javascript
mermaid.initialize({
  startOnLoad: true,
  theme: theme,
  securityLevel: 'loose',
  maxTextSize: 5000000,  // Increased for large diagrams
  maxEdges: 5000,        // Increased for complex graphs
  themeVariables: { ... },
  flowchart: { useMaxWidth: true, htmlLabels: true, curve: 'basis' }
});
```

**Theme-aware colors** for dark mode visibility:
- Lines: `#64b5f6` (bright blue)
- Node backgrounds: `#3a3a5c`
- Text: `#f5f5f5` (bright white)

